Package: regplanely
Title: Interactive Visualizations of Multiple Regression Models
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Will", "Hopper", , "whopper@smith.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7848-1946"))
Description: The regplanely package allows you to create an interactive visualization
    of a regression model's predictions using just a fitted model object. The visualization
    is created using the [plotly](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/plotly/index.html)
    library.
